snippet.title: Heated Battles Shooter
snippet.description:
Online Multiplayer shooting game. Game Mode isDeathmatch, Team Deathmatch, StrategyDomination, Gun Game,Domination. Al lgame modes have full bot support. Weapon is Assault Rifle(FAL), Pistol (M1911), Shotgun, Sniper (M40), FragGrenade, Flashbang, Smoke Grenade, Bat.

Space Area is added. You can fight in space shuttle factory, space laboratory building, and space control center. New gamemode DominationStrategy is added. One team must complete mission, for example making rocket, other team must foil that mission. Heated Battles there!

Many characters are added. captain, agent, spy, officer, belligerent, commander, and combatant. 

Heated Battles Shooter  download (Apple Store)
https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/heated-battles-shooter/id1543541925
